{"2971982":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:channel6","start":"1626473760","end":"1626479880","first":"L","idtitle":"LEKKERSTRAKANAAL","title":"Lekker Strak Anaal","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2Ff3ad95f3-5d06-455c-ab73-4399b1e55f4e,imi:82b27c9979e5f0d5cb5762306c7a1bd2883b6fe2","date":"2018","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/0c4__4f8__0c44f81a-39b1-4482-b9c9-571e45066697__B149197460.jpg","description":"Lien kent onze Kevin al wat langer. Ze vindt het heerlijk als hij haar anaal neemt in haar strakke jonge kontje. En extra lekker voor hem: hij mag zonder condoom in haar.","category":"Entertainment, Erotiek"},"2972934":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:channel6","start":"1626479880","end":"1626485100","first":"W","idtitle":"WESUMMONTHEDARKNESS","title":"We Summon the Darkness","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2Fb006880c-db55-4fa6-bffc-fe0931a95ab9,imi:28558b62ba6b4fdc03324c951866e37fad065290","date":"2019","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/377__e44__377e44ad-c414-4bd1-9973-2b6e81dabd76__B200176149.jpg","description":"Drie jonge vrouwen, Alexis, Bev en Val genaamd, zijn op weg naar een rockconcert. Ze ontmoeten daar drie veelbelovende muzikanten en belanden uiteindelijk gezamenlijk bij het huis van een van de drie vrouwen. De afterparty verloopt echter niet volgens plan.","category":"Film, Sciencefiction"},"2973872":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:channel6","start":"1626485100","end":"1626490200","first":"T","idtitle":"THESUPER","title":"The Super","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F907a9884-5a4d-4b92-8df6-8709f7285b25,imi:7c534912459624be2006c01cf70658579a092426","date":"2017","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/682__516__68251644-bd7e-4b9b-a101-efc82bae4f23__B171460358.jpg","description":"Voormalig agent Phil Lodge neemt een nieuwe baan aan als opzichter van een duur appartementencomplex in Manhattan. Wanneer huurders een voor een beginnen te verdwijnen, vreest Phil dat er een sadistische moordenaar door de gangen dwaalt en dat de levens van zijn dochters in gevaar zijn. Zijn hoofdverdachte is de vreemde klusjesman Walter.","category":"Film, Sciencefiction"},"2974803":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:channel6","start":"1626490200","end":"1626492000","first":"P","idtitle":"PLAYMOREHIGHLIGHTS","title":"Play More Highlights","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F9a694894-2a51-4d54-8870-991a42c89071,imi:90fbdcc61a08eea0f54edf7b350641c0b49e837d","date":"2021","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/3b2__ea6__3b2ea6f8-46e8-4f39-866f-4575e82a4b66__B182057900.jpg","description":"","category":"Nieuws, Actualiteitenprogramma's"},"2974894":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:channel6","start":"1626492000","end":"1626496080","first":"P","idtitle":"PLAYMOREHIGHLIGHTS","title":"Play More Highlights","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F9a694894-2a51-4d54-8870-991a42c89071,imi:c8d33d28124ee81223c859e82f434c2be44f8638","date":"2021","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/3b2__ea6__3b2ea6f8-46e8-4f39-866f-4575e82a4b66__B182057900.jpg","description":"","category":"Nieuws, Actualiteitenprogramma's"},"2975828":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:channel6","start":"1626496080","end":"1626500100","first":"P","idtitle":"PLAYMOREHIGHLIGHTS","title":"Play More Highlights","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F9a694894-2a51-4d54-8870-991a42c89071,imi:520c3cbc0927794802ef554a1a760dfe0d349df1","date":"2021","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/3b2__ea6__3b2ea6f8-46e8-4f39-866f-4575e82a4b66__B182057900.jpg","description":"","category":"Nieuws, Actualiteitenprogramma's"},"2976771":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:channel6","start":"1626500100","end":"1626504180","first":"P","idtitle":"